column3:
{
  "reasoning": "Three travelers meeting in the wilderness - this is exactly the kind of secretive gathering that hides heresy. The merchant probably peddles forbidden items, the mercenary sells their sword to protect sin, and that well-dressed one? Clearly up to no good. A bellowing announcement of my presence will set the proper tone - they should fear the Order's judgment before they even think of resisting. The Sacred Flame burns hot in my chest at this opportunity. They'll either prove their innocence through immediate submission, or reveal their guilt through defiance.",
  "verbal-interaction": {
    "content": "IN THE NAME OF THE ORDER OF CLEANSING LIGHT, HALT! All of you - stay exactly where you are! I am Sir Grimnar Ironhold, Hammer of the Sacred Flame, and you WILL explain what brings you to this remote place! Secretive meetings in the wilderness are the breeding grounds of heresy! The Order sees all, and I smell the stench of hidden sin upon this gathering!",
    "emotional_tone": "antagonism",
    "response-type": "speech"
  },
  "actions-taken": {
    "movement-action": {
      "primitive": "seek",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "target-type": "entity",
          "target-id": "merchant-group",
          "desired-distance": 2
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
